On macOS (and maybe BSDs, but I haven't tested), select returns -1 with errno=EINVAL if the value for timespec's microseconds amounts to more than a second, which makes the rtwizard regression tests time out. Compute the tv_sec and tv_usec members properly from refresh_rate
